# Transforming

Transforming examples
- Languages (translating, identifying language of text)
- Editing (spelling, grammar)
    - "Proofread and correct this text"
- Formats (e.g., HTML input, JSON output; markdown)
- Registers/formality ("translate into the formal and informal form")
- Tone transformation
    - "Translate the following from slang to a business letter"
    
Can get difference between original and modified with redlines
    - from redlines import Redlines
    - diff = Redlines(text, response)